      <title>霸菱信贷员工为了金钱和其他原因集体离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/barings-credit-staffers-left-en-masse-for-money-and-more-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的保拉·塞利格森 (Paula Seligson) 向 Vonnie Quinn 表示，金钱是 22 名巴林银行员工前往初创公司科林西亚全球管理有限公司 (Corinthia Global Management Ltd.) 离职的一个重要原因，但这并不是唯一的驱动因素，而且巴林银行的私人信贷业务陷入了混乱。彭博市场。” （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/barings-credit-staffers-left-en-masse-for-money-and-more-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:26:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Semler Scientific 股价因接受比特币财务策略而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/semler-scientific-shares-rise-on-embrace-of-bitcoin-treasury-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[医疗设备制造商 Semler Scientific Inc. 表示，该公司已采用比特币作为其主要储备资产，成为少数遵循 MicroStrategy Inc. 开创的有争议方法的上市公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/semler-scientific-shares-rise-on-embrace-of-bitcoin-treasury-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购融资渠道缩减，有利于信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/pipeline-for-acquisition-financing-shrinks-in-boon-for-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与几个月前相比，目前企业在长期债务市场上进行再融资的收购较少，这可能有助于提高今年的债券回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/pipeline-for-acquisition-financing-shrinks-in-boon-for-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
