      <title>先锋公司前首席执行官表示，联邦贸易委员会因埃克森美孚交易错误地诽谤了他</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/ex-pioneer-ceo-says-ftc-wrongly-vilified-him-over-exxon-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋自然资源公司前首席执行官斯科特·谢菲尔德表示，联邦监管机构歪曲了事实，错误地诽谤了他，称他试图与欧佩克勾结以支撑原油价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/ex-pioneer-ceo-says-ftc-wrongly-vilified-him-over-exxon-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特 (Elliott) 押注 25 亿美元重组德州仪器 (TI)</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/activist-elliott-takes-2-5-billion-texas-instruments-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 已向德州仪器公司 (Texas Instruments Inc.) 投资了超过 25 亿美元，并正在推动这家芯片制造商改善自由现金流，为这位颇具影响力的激进投资者的另一场行动奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/activist-elliott-takes-2-5-billion-texas-instruments-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:45:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>双拍卖需求不温不火后，国债扩大损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/treasuries-steady-before-debt-auction-rush-and-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二的两次美国政府债券拍卖吸引了不温不火的需求，导致交易商持有的票据比近期销售的数量更多，导致美国国债扩大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/treasuries-steady-before-debt-auction-rush-and-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债收益率在美国销售疲软后飙升：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国债券销售疲软后，美国国债下跌，股市波动，交易员也在权衡好坏参半的经济数据和美联储发言人的言论，这将有助于塑造利率前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 22:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
